HEADWORD: Unvulgarize
<hw>Un*vul"gar*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>vulgarize</ets>.]</ety> <def>To divest of
vulgarity; to make to be not vulgar.</def> <rj><au>Lamb.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
